<div class="jumbotron">
  <h1 class="display-4"><%= message %></h1>
  <p class="lead">Plan and organize your perfect outdoor gatherings with ease.</p>
  <hr class="my-4">
  <p>Create picnic events, manage guest lists, track items, and more with our simple and intuitive app.</p>
  <a class="btn btn-primary btn-lg" href="/picnics" role="button">View Picnics</a>
  <a class="btn btn-success btn-lg" href="/picnics/new" role="button">Create New Picnic</a>
</div>

<div class="row mt-5">
  <div class="col-md-4">
    <div class="card">
      <div class="card-body">
        <h5 class="card-title">Step 1: Create</h5>
        <p class="card-text">Create and organize picnic events with details like location, date, amenities and what you bring.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="col-md-4">
    <div class="card">
      <div class="card-body">
        <h5 class="card-title">Step 2: Share</h5>
        <p class="card-text">Share the picnic app link with friends so they can add their name, the items they will bring, and share the link further.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="col-md-4">
    <div class="card">
      <div class="card-body">
        <h5 class="card-title">Step 3: Enjoy</h5>
        <p class="card-text">Go to the location at the set time and enjoy a great picnic with all your friends!</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
